<seg id="375">By checking the financial or financial procedure tax authorities in the management of VAT and the use of VIES system have been found to be financial or. the tax authorities did not use sufficiently all VIES options and relevant legal permissions.</seg>
<seg id="376">It was also found that VIES did not provide up-to-date information on goods supply and validity of VAT registration in all cases.</seg>
<seg id="377">NKÚ SR compared data on the occurrence of erroneous data in SH, processed before the start of the inspection, with data processed after the completion of the inspection.</seg>
<seg id="378">From the comparison of these data it was apparent that the check of the NKÚ SR had an impact not only on the reduction in the number of SH with the wrongly mentioned ID, but also on the reduction of the number of unmixed errors in SH.</seg>
<seg id="379">In case of irregularities in reported NKÚ SR data, the tax authorities asked for local investigations or tax checks to be carried out.</seg>
