<seg id="381">The knowledge gained by the control actions showed that VIES provided tax administrators with the basic information necessary to check the correct application of VAT in intra-communitarian transactions.</seg>
<seg id="382">Since there is still room for tax evasion in this area, increased attention should be given to intracommunitary transactions when managing VAT.</seg>
