<seg id="27">The structure of the public procurement law in both countries</seg>
<seg id="28">In Germany, the process of European procurement procedures is governed by laws and regulations.</seg>
<seg id="29">The procurement procedure limited to Germany is governed by budgetary law and relevant administrative acts.</seg>
