<seg id="124">Prevention of corruption</seg>
<seg id="125">The importance of prevention of corruption</seg>
<seg id="126">There is no legal definition in any of both countries what corruption actually means.</seg>
<seg id="127">In general, corruption is seen as an abuse of a personal (confidential) position in its own favor.</seg>
