<seg id="63">Control number: KA-023/2016/1050</seg>
<seg id="64">Subject of control: Excise tax management</seg>
<seg id="65">Objective of the inspection: The aim of the inspection was to independent and objective examination whether FG SR and Customs (CÚ) in the management of excise duties operate economically, efficiently and effectively in accordance with general binding legislation.</seg>
<seg id="66">Controlled period: years 2012-2015</seg>
