<seg id="106">In addition to the appellant, a natural person who is a statutory body or is a member of the statutory body, or a natural person who is not the statutory body of the appellant or its member, must comply with the conditions of reliability and without debt, but exercises such activity (chain of legal persons in the position of a statutory body or of its member), so called. established entities).</seg>
