<seg id="100">3. Preparation and course of cooperation</seg>
<seg id="101">The first coordination meeting of representatives of the NKÚ-Czech Republic and representatives of the NKÚ SR, which discussed a specific cooperation procedure in the implementation of parallel checks in the field of excise taxes, took place in January 2006.</seg>
