<seg id="107">4. Comparison of the transportation of goods under the tax exemption regime</seg>
<seg id="108">NKÚ-Czech Republic handed over the Slovak side a database of transport ended in the Czech Republic, which contained a total of 5 items listed on accompanying documents, of which 5 738 items covered mineral oils, 134 items of alcohol and 4 items of tobacco products.</seg>
