<seg id="150">5. International exchange of information between the customs authorities of the Czech Republic and the SR</seg>
<seg id="151">Conditions of cooperation between the administrative authorities of the Member States responsible for the management of excise duties were adapted until 30. June 2005 by Council Directive 77/799 / EEC on mutual assistance between the competent authorities of the Member States in the field of direct taxes, certain excise duties and insurance taxes.</seg>
